1. RUN python3.9 -m venv flink_env

2. RUN source flink_env/bin/activate

3. Need to check: pip install apache-flink==1.18.0

4. cd ~ 

5. wget https://archive.apache.org/dist/flink/flink-1.18.0/flink-1.18.0-bin-scala_2.12.tgz

6. tar -xzf flink-1.18.0-bin-scala_2.12.tgz

7. vim ~/.bashrc

Set

export FLINK_HOME=/dir/to/flink-1.18.0
export PATH=$FLINK_HOME/bin:$PATH

9. source ~/.bashrc

8. Download from website: https://repo1.maven.org/maven2/org/apache/flink/flink-sql-connector-kafka/3.0.1-1.18/
- flink-sql-connector-kafka-3.0.1-1.18.jar
- copy this jar to $FLINK_HOME/lib

9. python flink_consumer.py